results.title: Thou Shalt Not Covet Thy Neighbor's Planet
results.description: While lecturing at a college about the legal aspects of relations with extra-terrestrials, DD comes up against some real aliens bent on world domination.

results.title: Fire and Ice in the Land of the Dead !
Heaven Is Knowing Who You Are
Who Is The Man In Black?
The Outsider
results.description: DD returns from Hell with his memories scrambled; Not knowing who he really is, he assumes the identity of Jack Murdock; Bullseye finds out about the confusion and decides to take advantage of the situation.

results.title: The Shadowman
results.description: Matt tries to figure out who he is while Bullseye hits the streets as Daredevil.

results.title: The Thief
results.description: Nyla begins training Matt how to be a thief; Bullseye starts stealing while wearing the Daredevil costume; Matt is hired as a boxer.

results.title: The Fighter
results.description: Bullseye decides to try his hand at being a hero; Kingpin goes to the fights and recognizes Matt Murdock in the ring.

results.title: The Student
results.description: Dreams of Elektra and Stick start to remind Matt of who he is; Kingpin contacts Bullseye for a special job.

results.title: The Hero
results.description: Kingpin has Nyla kidnapped and tells Matt to throw a fight to win her back; Matt refuses and wins the bout (just like dear old dad) and remembers who he is with the help of Urich.

results.title: Unmasked
results.description: Matt decides to propose to Karen but when she is kidnapped by The Boss to try and draw out Daredevil, he decides his lifestyle is too dangerous for domesticity and halts his plans.

results.title: Bullseye!
results.description: Matt dons the Bullseye costume to take down Bullseye wearing the DD duds.

results.title: Side By Side with the Ghost Rider
Through The Eyes Of The Enemy
Last Rites Part 1: The Termination of Typhoid !

results.title: The Owl, Ominous Overlord of Crime!
results.description: A wealthy and ruthless financier is exposed as a criminal and begins his reign as the Owl; The Owl hires Matt Murdock to get him out of his legal troubles; The Owl gathers a gang, traps DD and Karen and begins his bid to rule the underworld; DD escapes and takes the Owl down.

results.title: If There Should Be a Thunder God
results.description: With Cobra and Hyde on the loose, Matt decides to dress up like their prime antagonist, the mighty Thor, to draw them out; The real thunder god takes umbrage at being impersonated and battles DD; After proving that he is verily worthy, DD tangles with Cobra and Hyde and has his super-powered senses stolen by one of Hyde's formulas, making him truly blind.

results.title: Nocturnal Hunter
results.description: Daredevil faces an enhanced Owl who now has even more powers to make him like his namesake.

results.title: Dark And Deliverance
results.description: DD and the Owl have at it, but Owl finally decides to clean up his act.

results.title: Time Marks a Cry For Help
34 Hours
results.description: It's just another day in the life of old Hornhead.

results.title: Under The Knife
results.description: Daredevil convinces Spidey to go undercover to flush out a surgeon who is cutting up her dates for their organs.

results.title: Emergency Procedure
results.description: DD and Spidey put an end to the Surgeon General's macabre organ selling organization.

results.title: Dead Man's Hand Part 1: Blind Openers
results.description: Matt and Foggy go to Vegas to meet with mob bosses who want to hire them; After the lawyers decline the offer, Tombstone moves in for the kill; The major players in the maggia meet up to divide the fallen Kingpin's empire; Kingpin rides the subway in New York.

results.title: Dead Man's Hand Part 5: Dealing From The Bottom
results.description: The mob bosses continue to fight over the Kingpin's empire with DD caught in the crossfire.

results.title: Cards On The Table (Dead Man's Hand Part VII)
Blind Man's Bluff
results.description: A powerless and totally blind DD has to try and tackle the combined might of Mr. Hyde and Cobra.

results.title: Soul Search
results.description: Calypso turns DD into a living zombie and he has to fight to get out from under her control.
